{"tid":1163502,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"Bob叔 vs 慕容 ?","createTime":"2019-05-20T13:06:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-21T09:58:34.000Z","uid":197125,"like":84,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"857efc226323514e6be1cb956e97ee9f1da45b04","tid":1163502,"uid":197125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T13:06:57.000Z","msg":"啱啱睇晒三條片，bob叔有幾個point講得啱嘅，就係讀書有用、youtuber唔應該教人唔好讀書、唔鍾意讀書係個人選擇，將來唔好埋怨，但佢係有扭曲moyung講嘅嘢，而Moyung整條片最後嗰句先係重點「你一係有技能、一係人際關係、一係父幹，三樣嘢都冇就唔好諗住唔靠學歷」呢句都啱嘅，兩邊都有各自觀點，相反，Yaki整條片都冇觀點仲要覺得自己啱，Yaki真係收得皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nBtw moyung喺條片翻炒返佢一年前嘅片話「讀書發挖自己潛能興趣」，但bob叔同好多連登仔都話佢講過「讀書冇撚用」，想問問係邊一條片？"},{"pid":"fd89c353ca383c45af74a77d4a91838f60c64992","tid":1163502,"uid":228143,"like":14,"dislike":2,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T13:10:37.000Z","msg":"先定義咩係讀書<br />\n讀恒大算唔算讀書<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35543c7dcd6f6a0bc2869e1893a04582457c711b","tid":1163502,"uid":143878,"like":37,"dislike":46,"score":-9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T13:13:52.000Z","msg":"老老實實 你過我打手都係咁講架啦<br />\n睇完慕容條片覺得佢真係有道理<br />\n而且好明顯bob叔有d屌佢既論點的確係站不住腳<br />\n不過清高既連登仔點會click入去睇比佢賺view呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2999a35a2651e0ac5bba17289df167fac011f86d","tid":1163502,"uid":85586,"like":47,"dislike":7,"score":40,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T13:16:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/4JWF501sPc0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F4JWF501sPc0&d=RsYziF%2F%2FwXRI7aJQ3s5lGY429F%2FWQzM9xP7K%2BddLk1E%3D&h=2b146571\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/4JWF501sPc0</a><br />\n呢條片就已經完場啦<br />\n用做雞倫敦金去笑鳩人讀大學無用<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"051461f77991d8a56a48128bcf609da78db4e862","tid":1